<seg id="3">A THREE-point shooting barrage from Jermaine Beal in the first quarter helped the Perth Wildcats kill off Wollongong early on their way to an 87-47 rout at Perth Arena.</seg>
<seg id="4">The Cats celebrated their 500th all-time home game in style with a thumping win in front of a packed crowd to underline their status as title favourites early in the season.</seg>
