<seg id="42">Such a suggestion has already been made by Luigi Zingales of Chicago, an economist with impeccable right-wing credentials, who compared the current situation to that in the stock market prior to regulation FD, when public company executives could announce the earnings on a small conference call with a select group of analysts.</seg>
