<seg id="1">Diana Arbenina celebrated Halloween with her children</seg>
<seg id="2">Diana Arbenina does not hide what a huge pleasure she receives from upbringing her children.</seg>
<seg id="3">Despite the fact that right now Arbenina spends an especially large amount of time on creative work and social activity, she nonetheless finds the opportunity to busy oneself with Marta and Artyom, and not only spends time on their education, but also entertains them however possible.</seg>
