<seg id="1">Australian ARIA and APRA award winning musician Gotye in celebrity death hoax</seg>
<seg id="2">Gotye talks about the song writing process he used to create his smash hit song "Somebody That I Used to Know."</seg>
<seg id="3">Songwriter of the year ...</seg>
<seg id="4">Wally de Backer, aka Gotye, at the APRA Music Awards 2012.</seg>
<seg id="5">Picture: Adam Ward Source: The Daily Telegraph</seg>
<seg id="6">Gotye tells his fans on Twitter that he is not dead, despite internet rumours.</seg>
<seg id="7">AUSTRALIAN musician Gotye is not dead, despite internet reports and the flood of tweets from fans circulating about the rumour of his death.</seg>
