<seg id="1">Brett Whiteley painting sells for record $3,927,272</seg>
<seg id="2">Brett Whiteley's piece My Armchair, 1976, sells for $3,927,272.</seg>
<seg id="3">Photo: Jason South</seg>
<seg id="4">A record price was on Thursday night set for Australian artist Brett Whiteley for his stunning 1976 canvas My Armchair, detailing his beloved Lavender Bay studio, which fetched $3,927,272 including buyer's premium.</seg>
