<seg id="38">Flemington Race 3, No.</seg>
<seg id="39">Flemington trainer Nigel Blackiston is a former stable foreman for Bart Cummings so it is no surprise that he is a naturally patient man and this is highlighted by the career of his promising staying mare Let's Make A Deal, a four-year-old who has raced only 11 times.</seg>
