<seg id="44">SUGGESTED BET Although the barrier is awkward, Let's Make A Deal is a nice each-way bet.</seg>
<seg id="45">Flemington Race 5, No.</seg>
<seg id="46">The time-honoured Mackinnon Stakes used to be known as the "practice stakes"" by punters who got used to seeing Melbourne cup candidates have their lead-up run in the Mackinnon - and it was suggested that several were not out to bust their boilers.</seg>
<seg id="47">Not any more, not since the VRC increased the prizemoney to $1 million and re-classified it as a group 1 event.</seg>
