<seg id="61">As always this is a terrific race with several other chances, including the classy Red Tracer, Catkins and New Zealand visitor, Zonza.</seg>
<seg id="62">My numbers: 1, 3, 4, 14.</seg>
<seg id="63">Of the quaddie legs, this is the toughest.</seg>
<seg id="64">Straight racing at Flemington is always a test, with so many starters and guessing which part of the track will be best.</seg>
<seg id="65">The wind can often play a part too, so we'll go wide here, including a few at attractive odds.</seg>
