<seg id="1">Gunman Held As One Killed</seg>
<seg id="2">A security agent has been killed and three more people wounded after a man armed with a semi-automatic rifle opened fire inside Los Angeles International Airport.</seg>
<seg id="3">Police say the gunman pulled the weapon out of a bag and began firing near a security checkpoint at Terminal 3.</seg>
<seg id="4">An undated booking photo of Paul Ciancia</seg>
