<seg id="2">Mr Market has spoken.</seg>
<seg id="3">Royal Bank of Scotland is 8 per cent less attractive to investors after its long awaited strategic review than it was before.</seg>
<seg id="4">Given that the headline measure - an internal bad bank - is far less radical than some of the alternatives that were on offer, this is perhaps a surprising response.</seg>
