<seg id="21">I've made too many mistakes but I am going to continue to play aggressively out here because I have to make birdies to catch the lead.</seg>
<seg id="22">Hopefully I'll eliminate a few mistakes here or there.</seg>
<seg id="23">Rose's water trouble came on the last, the world number five thinning a bunker shot across the green and into the hazard on his way to a closing bogey and round of 71.</seg>
